message.entry: sliceViewer requires 3-D grayscale(MxNxP) or 3-D RGB volume(MxNxPx3) with no singleton dimensions.
The specified Parent is deleted or invalid.
The Parent property must be a figure or uipanel.
DisplayRangeInteraction is not supported for logical or RGB volumes.
Volume and Labels should be of the same size.
Number of values in {0} should be greater than or equal to max label value.
Valid browse directions for sliceViewer are 'X' or [1 0 0], 'Y' or [0 1 0] and 'Z' or [1 0 0]
